[{"text": "My travels to Afghanistan", "start": 15.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "began many, many years ago", "start": 18.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "on the eastern border of my country,", "start": 21.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "my homeland, Poland.", "start": 24.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I was walking through the forests", "start": 27.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of my grandmother's tales.", "start": 29.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "A land where every field hides a grave,", "start": 33.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "where millions of people", "start": 38.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "have been deported or killed", "start": 40.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in the 20th century.", "start": 43.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Behind the destruction,", "start": 46.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I found a soul of places.", "start": 48.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I met humble people.", "start": 51.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I heard their prayer", "start": 53.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and ate their bread.", "start": 55.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Then I have been walking East for 20 years --", "start": 57.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "from Eastern Europe to Central Asia --", "start": 62.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "through the Caucasus Mountains,", "start": 65.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Middle East,", "start": 67.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "North Africa,", "start": 69.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Russia.", "start": 71.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And I ever met more humble people.", "start": 73.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "And I shared their bread and their prayer.", "start": 77.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This is why I went to Afghanistan.", "start": 80.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "One day, I crossed the bridge", "start": 83.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "over the Oxus River.", "start": 87.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I was alone on foot.", "start": 89.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And the Afghan soldier was so surprised to see me", "start": 91.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that he forgot to stamp my passport.", "start": 93.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But he gave me a cup of tea.", "start": 96.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And I understood", "start": 98.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that his surprise was my protection.", "start": 100.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So I have been walking and traveling,", "start": 103.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "by horses, by yak, by truck, by hitchhiking,", "start": 106.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "from Iran's border", "start": 109.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to the bottom, to the edge of the Wakhan Corridor.", "start": 111.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "And in this way", "start": 116.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I could find noor, the hidden light of Afghanistan.", "start": 118.26, "duration": 7.0}, {"text": "My only weapon", "start": 125.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "was my notebook and my Leica.", "start": 127.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "I heard prayers of the Sufi --", "start": 132.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "humble Muslims,", "start": 134.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "hated by the Taliban.", "start": 136.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Hidden river,", "start": 138.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "interconnected with the mysticism", "start": 140.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from Gibraltar to India.", "start": 142.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The mosque where the respectful foreigner", "start": 145.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "is showered with blessings", "start": 150.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and with tears,", "start": 152.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and welcomed as a gift.", "start": 155.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "What do we know", "start": 159.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "about the country and the people", "start": 161.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we pretend to protect,", "start": 163.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "about the villages", "start": 166.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "where the only one medicine", "start": 169.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to kill the pain and to stop the hunger", "start": 171.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is opium?", "start": 173.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "These are opium-addicted people", "start": 175.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "on the roofs of Kabul", "start": 178.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "10 years after the beginning of our war.", "start": 181.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "These are the nomad girls", "start": 185.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "who became prostitutes for Afghan businessmen.", "start": 188.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "What do we know about the women", "start": 192.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "10 years after the war?", "start": 194.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Clothed in this nylon bag,", "start": 196.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "made in China,", "start": 198.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with the name of burqa.", "start": 200.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "I saw one day,", "start": 204.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the largest school in Afghanistan,", "start": 206.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "a girls' school.", "start": 209.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "13,000 girls", "start": 211.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "studying here", "start": 214.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "in the rooms underground,", "start": 218.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "full of scorpions.", "start": 221.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And their love [for studying]", "start": 224.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "was so big that I cried.", "start": 227.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "What do we know", "start": 232.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "about the death threats by the Taliban", "start": 234.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "nailed on the doors", "start": 237.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of the people who dare to send their daughters to school as in Balkh?", "start": 239.26, "duration": 6.0}, {"text": "The region is not secure, but full of the Taliban,", "start": 245.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and they did it.", "start": 248.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "My aim is to give a voice", "start": 250.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to the silent people,", "start": 252.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to show the hidden lights", "start": 255.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "behind the curtain of the great game,", "start": 259.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the small worlds ignored by the media", "start": 262.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and the prophets of a global conflict.", "start": 265.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Thanks.", "start": 267.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 269.26, "duration": 9.0}]